      "fileName": "index.html",
      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>新闻聚合应用 - 首页</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            background-color: #f4f4f4;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: #2c3e50;\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 15px 20px;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 24px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 15px;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: #fff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        .filters {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            gap: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .filters button {\n            padding: 8px 15px;\n            border: none;\n            background-color: #3498db;\n            color: #fff;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .filters button:hover {\n            background-color: #2980b9;\n        }\n\n        .news-list {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .news-card {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .news-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n        }\n\n        .news-card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 180px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n        }\n\n        .news-card .content {\n            padding: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .news-card h3 {\n            font-size: 18px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .news-card .meta {\n            font-size: 14px;\n            color: #777;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .news-card a {\n            display: inline-block;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n            color: #3498db;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: #2c3e50;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 15px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .user-status {\n            font-size: 14px;\n            color: #ccc;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 600px) {\n            nav {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                align-items: flex-start;\n            }\n\n            .filters {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                align-items: flex-start;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n    <script>\n        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {\n            const buttons = document.querySelectorAll('.filters button');\n            buttons.forEach(button => {\n                button.addEventListener('click', () => {\n                    buttons.forEach(btn => btn.classList.remove('active'));\n                    button.classList.add('active');\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>新闻聚合应用</h1>\n        <nav>\n            <a href=\"login.html\">登录</a>\n            <a href=\"register.html\">注册</a>\n            <a href=\"profile.html\">个人中心</a>\n        </nav>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"user-status\">\n            当前用户：未登录（<a href=\"login.html\">点击登录</a>）\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"filters\">\n            <button>热门</button>\n            <button>科技</button>\n            <button>体育</button>\n            <button>国际</button>\n            <button>财经</button>\n            <button>娱乐</button>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"news-list\">\n            <div class=\"news-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x180\" alt=\"新闻图片\">\n                <div class=\"content\">\n                    <h3>全球气候峰会召开</h3>\n                    <div class=\"meta\">来源：新华社 · 2023-10-15</div>\n                    <p>全球气候峰会于今日在北京举行，多国领导人出席并发表重要讲话...</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\">查看详情</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"news-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x180\" alt=\"新闻图片\">\n                <div class=\"content\">\n                    <h3>中国男篮晋级世界杯四强</h3>\n                    <div class=\"meta\">来源：腾讯体育 · 2023-10-15</div>\n                    <p>中国男篮在世界杯比赛中表现出色，成功晋级四强...</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\">查看详情</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"news-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x180\" alt=\"新闻图片\">\n                <div class=\"content\">\n                    <h3>美联储宣布加息</h3>\n                    <div class=\"meta\">来源：路透社 · 2023-10-15</div>\n                    <p>美联储宣布再次加息，影响全球经济走势...</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\">查看详情</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        &copy; 2023 新闻聚合应用. 保留所有权利。\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>",
      "type": "prototype_file"
    },
