      "fileName": "subscriptions.html",
      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>订阅管理页 - 新闻聚合应用</title>\n  <style>\n    body {\n      margin: 0;\n      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n      background-color: #f4f6f8;\n      color: #333;\n    }\n\n    header {\n      background-color: #1a73e8;\n      color: white;\n      padding: 15px 20px;\n      display: flex;\n      justify-content: space-between;\n      align-items: center;\n    }\n\n    header h1 {\n      margin: 0;\n      font-size: 1.5rem;\n    }\n\n    nav a {\n      color: white;\n      margin-left: 15px;\n      text-decoration: none;\n      font-weight: bold;\n    }\n\n    main {\n      padding: 20px;\n      max-width: 900px;\n      margin: auto;\n    }\n\n    h2 {\n      margin-bottom: 10px;\n      color: #1a73e8;\n    }\n\n    .subscription-list {\n      display: flex;\n      flex-wrap: wrap;\n      gap: 10px;\n      margin-bottom: 20px;\n    }\n\n    .topic-tag {\n      background-color: #e8f0fe;\n      border: 1px solid #bdcdd9;\n      color: #1a73e8;\n      padding: 8px 16px;\n      border-radius: 20px;\n      font-size: 0.95rem;\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: space-between;\n      cursor: pointer;\n      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n    }\n\n    .topic-tag:hover {\n      background-color: #d2e3fc;\n    }\n\n    .topic-tag .remove-btn {\n      margin-left: 10px;\n      color: #d9534f;\n      font-weight: bold;\n      cursor: pointer;\n    }\n\n    .add-section {\n      margin-top: 20px;\n    }\n\n    .available-tags {\n      display: flex;\n      flex-wrap: wrap;\n      gap: 10px;\n    }\n\n    .available-tag {\n      background-color: #f1f3f4;\n      border: 1px solid #ddd;\n      color: #5f6368;\n      padding: 8px 16px;\n      border-radius: 20px;\n      font-size: 0.95rem;\n      cursor: pointer;\n      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n    }\n\n    .available-tag:hover {\n      background-color: #e0e0e0;\n    }\n\n    footer {\n      background-color: #f1f3f4;\n      text-align: center;\n      padding: 15px;\n      font-size: 0.9rem;\n      color: #777;\n      margin-top: 40px;\n    }\n\n    @media (max-width: 600px) {\n      .available-tags, .subscription-list {\n        flex-direction: column;\n        align-items: flex-start;\n      }\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <header>\n    <h1>新闻聚合应用</h1>\n    <nav>\n      <a href=\"index.html\">首页</a>\n      <a href=\"login.html\">登录</a>\n      <a href=\"register.html\">注册</a>\n    </nav>\n  </header>\n\n  <main>\n    <h2>我的订阅主题</h2>\n    <p>您可以查看、添加或删除感兴趣的新闻主题。</p>\n\n    <div class=\"subscription-list\" id=\"subscriptionList\">\n      <div class=\"topic-tag\" data-topic=\"科技\">\n        科技 <span class=\"remove-btn\">&times;</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"topic-tag\" data-topic=\"体育\">\n        体育 <span class=\"remove-btn\">&times;</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"topic-tag\" data-topic=\"财经\">\n        财经 <span class=\"remove-btn\">&times;</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"add-section\">\n      <h2>添加订阅</h2>\n      <p>选择您感兴趣的主题：</p>\n      <div class=\"available-tags\">\n        <div class=\"available-tag\">国际</div>\n        <div class=\"available-tag\">娱乐</div>\n        <div class=\"available-tag\">军事</div>\n        <div class=\"available-tag\">健康</div>\n        <div class=\"available-tag\">教育</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </main>\n\n  <footer>\n    &copy; 2023 新闻聚合应用. 保留所有权利。\n  </footer>\n\n  <script>\n    // 删除订阅标签\n    document.querySelectorAll('.remove-btn').forEach(btn => {\n      btn.addEventListener('click', function () {\n        this.closest('.topic-tag').remove();\n      });\n    });\n\n    // 添加订阅标签\n    document.querySelectorAll('.available-tag').forEach(tag => {\n      tag.addEventListener('click', function () {\n        const topicName = this.textContent;\n        const existing = document.querySelector(`.topic-tag[data-topic=\\\"${topicName}\\\"]`);\n        if (!existing) {\n          const newTag = document.createElement('div');\n          newTag.className = 'topic-tag';\n          newTag.dataset.topic = topicName;\n          newTag.innerHTML = `\n            ${topicName} \n            <span class=\"remove-btn\">&times;</span>\n          `;\n          document.getElementById('subscriptionList').appendChild(newTag);\n\n          newTag.querySelector('.remove-btn').addEventListener('click', function () {\n            newTag.remove();\n          });\n        }\n      });\n    });\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>",
      "type": "prototype_file"
    },
